All My Love (Korean: ) is a South Korean situation comedy. Starring Kim Gab Soo, Park Mi-Sun, Jo Kwon, Ga-in, Yoon Doo Joon, Jun Tae Soo and Yoon Seung Ah. It began broadcasting on November 8, 2010 on MBC and its final episode was aired on September 16, 2011. The story of the relationship between two families, based on Kongji and Patzzi, the traditional Korean Cinderella folktale about Kongji and Patji. The Kongji family is poor but kind, while the Patji family is rich but selfish.
